    <item>
      <title>侮辱性总统在克罗地亚选举中给欧盟带来风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/croatia-election-insult-hurling-president-milanovic-threatens-eu-unity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克罗地亚总统佐兰·米拉诺维奇反对北约东扩，并谴责对乌克兰的军事援助是延长与俄罗斯战争的“极不道德”的道路。现在他想在周三的选举中接管政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/croatia-election-insult-hurling-president-milanovic-threatens-eu-unity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肖尔茨表示他将在习近平会谈中提高乌克兰贸易规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/scholz-says-he-ll-raise-trade-rules-ukraine-as-xi-talks-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨表示，在与中国领导人习近平的会谈开始之际，他将提出贸易规则、俄罗斯乌克兰战争和气候问题，这突显出两国必须解决的问题越来越多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/scholz-says-he-ll-raise-trade-rules-ukraine-as-xi-talks-start</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 03:39:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的筹款显示出对石油行业和富裕捐助者的依赖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/election-2024-campaign-finance-trump-relies-on-small-group-of-rich-donors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普依靠一小部分捐助者贡献了他三月份筹款的很大一部分，这表明他转向富有的捐助者来为他的总统竞选提供资金的早期成功。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/election-2024-campaign-finance-trump-relies-on-small-group-of-rich-donors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 02:06:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡李显龙为下一任总理黄之锋铺平道路，观察家们怎么说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/singapore-s-lee-paves-way-for-wong-after-20-years-as-pm-voices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡总理李显龙将于 5 月 15 日卸任，任职二十年后。 72 岁的李将把权力移交给 51 岁的副手劳伦斯·黄 (Lawrence Wong)，这一交接被广泛报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/singapore-s-lee-paves-way-for-wong-after-20-years-as-pm-voices</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 01:49:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
