      <title>美国特使前往朝鲜边境继续向平壤施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/us-envoy-heads-to-korean-border-to-keep-pressure-on-pyongyang</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻联合国大使前往分隔朝韩两国的非军事区，批评平壤危及和平，并邀请其重返陷入僵局的核裁军谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/us-envoy-heads-to-korean-border-to-keep-pressure-on-pyongyang</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 23:46:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪为全国投票前取消的选举债券辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/modi-defends-scrapped-electoral-bonds-ahead-of-national-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理纳伦德拉·莫迪为通过选举债券提供政治资金进行了辩护，但印度最高法院在裁定这种不透明工具违宪后取消了选举债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/modi-defends-scrapped-electoral-bonds-ahead-of-national-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 15:18:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>悉尼教堂礼拜中发生刺伤事件，男子被警方逮捕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-15/urgent-police-say-a-man-is-arrested-after-a-reported-stabbing-at-a-church-in-sydney</link>
      <description><![CDATA[悉尼（美联社）——澳大利亚警方表示，悉尼在一次教堂礼拜期间发生持刀袭击事件，导致一名主教和一名牧师受伤，震惊的信徒在网上和现场观看，并引发了骚乱，这是一种恐怖主义行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-15/urgent-police-say-a-man-is-arrested-after-a-reported-stabbing-at-a-church-in-sydney</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 11:27:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
